column2: 111Cute Duck Feet Ceramic Bowl, Animal Statue Handmade Table Art Sculpture Decorative Bowl for Sundries, Multifunctional as Key Bowl, Fruit Bowl, Candy Bowl, Jewelry Organizer and Cat and Dog Food Bowl
Design: This modern minimalist style decorative bowl for home decor is designed to bring a little young at heart. With its cute small duck tail and duck feet, we hope it can light up your day.
Material: Cast and handicraft by ceramic, the surface is coated with water-base non-toxic paint, has a sturdy, smooth touch. Non-slip pats on the duck feet make it suitable for any surface.

Multifunction: Can be used as bedroom decor, coffee table decor, kitchen decor, entryway table decor, funny office decor, nightstand decor, bathroom decor, dog and cat food bowl, halloween candy bowl.
Occasion: Perfect gift idea for holiday and as birthday gift, wedding gift, house warming gift, sister gift, off to college essentials and it can also be the special present for your lovely pet.
Size: This unique home decor is 6.69*5.09*7.09inch / 17*15*18cm (L*W*H) and the diameter of the opening is 5.12inch / 13cm.
The Cute Duck Feet Ceramic Bowl is A Displaying Center Piece to Storage Small Items
